column5: 7:30 am Sunday heavy north wind made for some uncomfortable fishing for my son. 8:45 am Monday and the lake is like glass as I drive to work and he is on his first ever school bus ride.      First trip on the school bus, second day of jk.

Sounds like fishing... Its a shame but a lesson learned about fishing at a young age i guess. Last three times i managed to get out the weather was terrible and fishing was dead slow. Now that im at work its ideal! It sucks!!!

such is the way, driving by lake o today on the skyway and it was glass, looked perfect, we got out Saturday evening but it was a little too choppy and the fish had disappeared so it was a short venture unfortunately
